# AI Code Review Buddy Development Rules

## Project Context
Building an AI-powered code review assistant that provides feedback on code quality, best practices, and potential issues.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React with TypeScript
- Backend: Node.js/Express or Python/FastAPI
- AI: OpenAI API (GPT-4)
- Database: SQLite for simplicity (upgrade later if needed)

## Code Standards
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Follow TDD approach where possible
- Keep components small and focused
- Prioritize code readability

## AI Assistant Instructions
- Break down complex tasks into smaller steps
- Always consider error handling
- Suggest tests for new features
- Keep AI prompts versioned and testable 